    whyThis: "Day 1 is about seeing the full picture of what a PIP has disrupted — not just the work part. Being placed on a performance improvement plan can ripple into many areas at once: your sense of competence, your trust in the people around you, your financial security, even how you feel walking into the office. Most people fixate on one area (usually 'Can I meet the requirements?') while other disruptions quietly build. This inventory maps seven areas so you can see where you actually are right now — honestly, without spinning. It becomes your baseline. You'll come back to these same seven areas on Day 24 to see what shifted.",
