    whyNow: "The best early contributions are not about proving you belong. They are about delivering genuine value that builds trust and credibility.",
    science: "Structured early-win selection engages the prefrontal cortex's planning circuits to evaluate potential contributions against multiple criteria (visibility, alignment, achievability, values-consistency). This prevents the anxiety-driven over-delivery that undermines new-role transitions.",
    instruction: "For each scenario, choose between two early-win options. Consider: visibility, manager alignment, achievability, and values consistency. Trust your strategic instinct — the pattern of your choices reveals your priorities.",
